---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const title = "Privacy Policy | Des Moines Septic";
const description = "Privacy policy for desmoinesseptic.com.";
---
<Layout {title} {description}>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:820px">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p><em>Last updated: May 2026</em></p>
      <p>This Privacy Policy describes how Des Moines Septic ("we", "us", "our") collects, uses, and shares information about you when you visit desmoinesseptic.com or request service through our forms.</p>
      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you submit a service request, we collect: your name, phone number, email address (if provided), service address or city, and a description of the service you need. We also collect basic technical data automatically through standard web analytics: IP address, browser type, pages viewed, and referral source.</p>
      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use your contact information solely to respond to your service request, schedule and dispatch service, and follow up on completed work. We may use aggregated, anonymized analytics data to improve our website.</p>
      <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell your information. We share your information only with service providers we use to operate the business (for example, our web hosting and form delivery platforms) and where required by law.</p>
      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use basic cookies for analytics and to remember user preferences. You can disable cookies through your browser settings; this site will continue to function.</p>
      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of personal information we hold about you by contacting us through our <a href="/contact/">contact form</a> or by calling (515) 303-4896.</p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this policy? Use our <a href="/contact/">contact form</a> or call (515) 303-4896.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
